    "long_instructions": "#### Debugging with Rafa\r\n\r\nRafa is trying to get all of his sounds to play together in a certain sequence and match the timeline below. Can you help him **debug** his code so it matches the example? **Debugging** is the process of finding bugs and fixing them so everything works like you'd expect!\r\n\r\nYou only need to rearrange Rafa's blocks to complete this level! You don't need to add anything new!\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/4c7a3555aad6bd76c357cc26db5addd8-image-1742938962341.png)",
